{"name":"Calm The Wild Beast","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your soothing and hypnotic voice calms one animal within 48 yards (24 squares) unless it makes a successful Will Power Test. You may approach the beast and touch it without fear; it remains placid. If a mount, you may ride it with a +10% bonus to any Ride Skill Tests you are required to make. The animal remains friendly towards you for a number of hours equal to your Magic Characteristic unless you unless you attack it, in which case the enchantment is broken immediately.&nbsp;</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"48"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":5},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A lump of sugar","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"2qs6RLRVYxSbpMMm"}
{"name":"The Beast Unleashed","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You unleash the primal savagery of your allies. Any friendly character within 12 yards (6 squares) of you goes into a frenzy, as per the talent of that name. No roll is required; they become frenzied as soon as the spell is cast. This spell does not work on animals (they are already beasts!).</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"12"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":19},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"2 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A wolf ’s heart","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"B722QzzWBUstCbvr"}
{"name":"Master's Voice","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You command one animal within 24 yards (12 squares) to do your bidding unless it makes a successful Will Power Test. On its next turn, you decide what actions the animal will take and it will do as you command.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"24"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":13},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A miniature whip made of braided animal hair","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"CVFKAyWyvP9WMxOE"}
{"name":"Crow's Feast","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You summon up a murder of supernatural crows anywhere within 48 yards (24 squares) that swoops down upon your enemies. These are Aethyric creatures of vengeance, with iron-shod beaks and bleeding feathers. They may be summoned anywhere, as they are capable of passing through any form of non-sentient material—trees, rocks, metal etc. These “crows” always appear in huge flocks—use the large template to represent this. Those affected take a Damage 3 hit from the furious crows, which then scatter as quickly as they appeared. Do not roll for hit location; all hits are to the head.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"48"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":"3"},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":17},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A caged crow","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"HMfQOnqARL3wV678"}
{"name":"Form Of The Raging Bear","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You transform yourself (and all the equipment you are carrying) into a bear for up to 1 hour. You retain your mental faculties and your Intelligence and Will Power. Your other stats are as a bear. You cannot talk or use magic while in bear form. You may end this spell at any time and resume your normal form. The spell ends automatically if you take a Critical Hit.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":21},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"3 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A bear’s claw","bonus":3},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"KeP0wEbANe9WnCM9"}
{"name":"Claws Of Fury","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>Your fingernails turn into razor sharp claws as you take on a feral aspect. You gain +1 to your Attacks Characteristic and a +10% bonus to Weapon Skill and your claws count as hand weapons with the Fast Quality. Claws of fury lasts a number of minutes equal to your Magic Characteristic. You cannot wield a weapon while claws of fury is in effect.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":8},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A cat's claw","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"Mj2paeki5j1xJjTh"}
{"name":"Form Of The Soaring Raven","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You transform yourself (and all the equipment you are carrying) into a raven for up to 1 hour. You retain your mental faculties and your Intelligence and Will Power. Your other stats are as a raven. You cannot talk or use magic while in raven form. You may end this spell at any time and resume your normal form. The spell ends automatically if you take a Critical Hit.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":7},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Full Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A raven feather","bonus":1},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"Upe7QRCZzIeVm7DH"}
{"name":"The Talking Beast","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>If you cast this spell immediately before taking on animal form, you can speak while so transformed. You can also cast this spell on an animal within 24 yards (12 squares) to gift it with the power of speech for a number of minutes equal to your Magic Characteristic.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":"24"},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":11},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"Half Action"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A tongue from the animal you are changing into","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"Wz5jdx9adM8qBjHl"}
{"name":"Form Of The Ravening Wolf","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You transform yourself (and all the equipment you are carrying) into a wolf for up to 1 hour. You retain your mental faculties and your Intelligence and Will Power. Your other stats are as a wolf. You cannot talk or use magic while in wolf form. You may end this spell at any time and resume your normal form. The spell ends automatically if you take a Critical Hit.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":15},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"2 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A wolf ’s paw","bonus":2},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"jJ6hz2TmFpwfSwxx"}
{"name":"Wings Of The Falcon","permission":{"default":0,"Rx67OhO2NrPonOlY":3},"type":"spell","data":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":"<p>You grow wings from your back, which are strong enough to bear you aloft. You can fly for a number of minutes equal to your Magic Characteristic with a Flying Movement of 4. Obviously, simple folk, seeing someone so transformed by wings of the falcon, will assume that you are some form of Chaos Daemon and react appropriately.</p>"},"gmdescription":{"type":"String","label":"Description","value":""},"lore":{"type":"String","label":"Lore","value":"Arcane Lore (Beasts)"},"range":{"type":"String","label":"Range","value":""},"damage":{"type":"String","label":"Damage","value":""},"cn":{"type":"Number","label":"Casting Number","value":25},"time":{"type":"String","label":"Casting Time","value":"2 Full Actions"},"magicMissile":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Magic Missile","value":false},"ingredient":{"type":"String","label":"Ingredient","value":"A live falcon","bonus":3},"template":{"value":""}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/wfrp2e/icons/blank.png","_id":"xOY0bcby9T4WBdHo"}
